  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled, multicentre clinical trial to
      assess the efficacy and tolerability of natural seawater based throat spray among adult
      patients with acute sore throat.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
